        {
            "title": "均勝電子料去年純利增長約40.56%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">均勝電子(00699)發盈喜，預期2025年度實現歸袰公司股東淨利潤約13.5億元(人民幣．下同)，按年增長40.56%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：均勝電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250120_FI_source-web_Joyson.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：均勝電子官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250120_FI_source-web_Joyson.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：均勝電子官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司又估計，去年實現歸屬於公司股東並扣除非經常性損益後淨利潤，約達15億元，按年增<br/>  長約17.02%。期內盈利提升，主要受惠於公司採取各項盈利改善和業務整合措施，在全球各業務區域逐步取得成效，海外盈利能力持續恢復。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15614598-%e5%9d%87%e5%8b%9d%e9%9b%bb%e5%ad%90%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7%e7%b4%8440-56",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/Joyson-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 09:12:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
